字副作用又大</blockquote>家計會有幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係有賣廣告果隻 <br />\n副作用大 講咗幾多年 唔整細副作用 邊條女會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打喺家計會買？上次我上去問個姑娘叫我唔好食佢地嗰d 好撚老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a42433aeeab434f477b91cc47c5390d635b19c","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/142258_432b086ef92fb158173598f52b9cacef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F142258_432b086ef92fb158173598f52b9cacef.jpg&h=e8313beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生俾左哩隻我 絲打食緊邊隻？"},{"pid":"0b2f59b03b742adb6f7dd502bc1de5329fa1d39a","tid":529751,"uid":78349,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有keep住食 皮光肉滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>食邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYaz"},{"pid":"c5db5c972c7d6fc38bddf5ec7500b8fb4998c4a1","tid":529751,"uid":78349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/142258_432b086ef92fb158173598f52b9cacef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F142258_432b086ef92fb158173598f52b9cacef.jpg&h=e8313beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生俾左哩隻我 絲打食緊邊隻？</blockquote><br />\n你呢隻舊藥 食左好似易肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991bd0fe5c3d9181dbbce6f8ce449a77ea2e1bf8","tid":529751,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35409c508d12fabae8520ca5ccd3c678680b90e7","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問左醫生 哩隻係新藥 除左基本避孕主治暗倉<br />\n唔好去家計會買 得個平字副作用又大</blockquote>家計會有幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係有賣廣告果隻 <br />\n副作用大 講咗幾多年 唔整細副作用 邊條女會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打喺家計會買？上次我上去問個姑娘叫我唔好食佢地嗰d 好撚老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"我男人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上 佢同出邊賣既一樣 正如安全套 佢仲要成本價 但同佢買要見佢<br />\n<br />\n點解呢個名會有人認為係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係果幾間廠出 貴d個副作用比較小d 但所謂肥呀 之類既野都係唔會大機會有<br />\n<br />\n避孕藥係黃酮素 有d足廿八日 黎經果時食果堆係鐵質丸 補血用 <br />\n<br />\n止暗瘡實際係治標唔治本"},{"pid":"a1e37266e08a62b9d9350e8de96a77e2c503e27e","tid":529751,"uid":10142,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"食左就黎兩個月<br />\n皮膚冇問題 仲好似好左<br />\n對波又大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cea09a3df5a5e60df6ad187672eeeb04305b185","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/142258_432b086ef92fb158173598f52b9cacef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F142258_432b086ef92fb158173598f52b9cacef.jpg&h=e8313beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生俾左哩隻我 絲打食緊邊隻？</blockquote><br />\n你呢隻舊藥 食左好似易肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩隻既新藥出既新藥"},{"pid":"d78c0a284d191f5023b2d2adc6aa5243283bfcb3","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左就黎兩個月<br />\n皮膚冇問題 仲好似好左<br />\n對波又大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打食邊隻？"},{"pid":"ee38a87a6cba7a48c86c591050a9d0c7ec4059e3","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問左醫生 哩隻係新藥 除左基本避孕主治暗倉<br />\n唔好去家計會買 得個平字副作用又大</blockquote>家計會有幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係有賣廣告果隻 <br />\n副作用大 講咗幾多年 唔整細副作用 邊條女會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打喺家計會買？上次我上去問個姑娘叫我唔好食佢地嗰d 好撚老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我男人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實際上 佢同出邊賣既一樣 正如安全套 佢仲要成本價 但同佢買要見佢<br />\n<br />\n點解呢個名會有人認為係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係果幾間廠出 貴d個副作用比較小d 但所謂肥呀 之類既野都係唔會大機會有<br />\n<br />\n避孕藥係黃酮素 有d足廿八日 黎經果時食果堆係鐵質丸 補血用 <br />\n<br />\n止暗瘡實際係治標唔治本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咩？我都係聽醫生講 佢俾我嗰隻係第四代<br />\n家計會嗰d係第一二代<br />\n<br />\n其實係減左劑量 因為好小已經可以達到避孕效果<br />\n反而係睇其他需要揀黎食<br />\n我食21粒既 都係諗住試幾個月去完旅行就唔食<br />\n順便睇下皮膚有無好到"},{"pid":"45ccb486e823cd4f274b4e6d8326a5b5c80ad94e","tid":529751,"uid":61649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"我成年冇黎m搞到要食黎調經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22ad302f20b16502a07b1886c8db46777e8f86b","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成年冇黎m搞到要食黎調經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成年唔黎 有無殘得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"