":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"有次趕住時間食，冇水喺身邊<br />\n用口水吞落去 然後再飲咗杯茶 <br />\n咁樣有冇問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37586172c3b8d0a7981c636fda6c716eb60a16af","tid":529751,"uid":67596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35409c508d12fabae8520ca5ccd3c678680b90e7","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問左醫生 哩隻係新藥 除左基本避孕主治暗倉<br />\n唔好去家計會買 得個平字副作用又大</blockquote>家計會有幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係有賣廣告果隻 <br />\n副作用大 講咗幾多年 唔整細副作用 邊條女會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打喺家計會買？上次我上去問個姑娘叫我唔好食佢地嗰d 好撚老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"家計會有好多款㗎啵 新又有 舊又有<br />\n新姐係你萬寧見到有嗰啲 優思明 優悅依種最新最少副作用嘅避孕藥<br />\n我食緊優思明 藥房賣成$18x 家計會都只係一百幾"},{"pid":"946f35b7b7b8ea93ab89b2d46b016ea36317be31","tid":529751,"uid":12455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"719c811aa1ed5f5f7cf18182ecf2764a902476f4","tid":529751,"uid":140694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"有次趕住時間食，冇水喺身邊<br />\n用口水吞落去 然後再飲咗杯茶 <br />\n咁樣有冇問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"應該冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：大部分時間都用口水吞"},{"pid":"a67c441b49dad908e995e0b445f19cb38e5baf4b","tid":529751,"uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"我係巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近女朋友主動話食藥，但叫我幫佢買<br />\n我女朋友係屬於容易水腫同易肥，我擔心佢食左有副作用<br />\n絲打可唔可以介紹一個比較好同安全嘅牌子比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d61159ccf6684236f13dc601df583c6d7ac062","tid":529751,"uid":26052,"lik