","msg":"你係咪打左三個月個枝針？一個月打一次個隻唔會咁<br />\n三個月打一枝先會耐啲黎"},{"pid":"289ca466e869100b49e44150c64714653c21f3dd","tid":529751,"uid":166749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3b7c971d7ac0ea643c2e2c1158353bcf830372","tid":529751,"uid":155325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"食左一個月 皮膚冇好過 瘡照爆 唔食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥有適應期架，繼續食先會好"},{"pid":"ef8da02707d4abeaae02cf0baa2bfab134ac025f","tid":529751,"uid":22902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11bcb129ba93425f766009fed4e8d8596ace7b3","tid":529751,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"食左年幾兩年，食loette<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0377be433dc5f558211788f9f2fa9e3d646b999","tid":529751,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"試下yasmin"},{"pid":"be09374e98be10e2b5ca50c25f2790c39e70c158","tid":529751,"uid":64930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"前年10月第一次食避孕藥結果日日keep住流m唔停<br />\n又唔敢唔食，食左兩個星期流到入埋醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓左係婦科兩日，個醫生話要食灑成排完左一個週期先停得藥，寫紙比我買第二隻藥<br />\n<br />\n結果我一停就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此m恢復正常，但因為咁每半年要去醫院覆一次診比張黎經記錄佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b7b8ffb2c0349c7cfcc0a014d708a62115ce38","tid":529751,"uid":132684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹想問 可以點樣唔理性討論避孕藥？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如d on9仔入黎話我係雞"},{"pid":"f909a494d314473087722a00011915038aebe194","tid":529751,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s